title: War of the Roses: A Timestamp from 2 Months Ago
description: Ashley's boyfriend Daniel went to quarantine with his mom in Rapid City but then he friend swears she saw him at a grocery store in town.  So now Ashley is questioning if he's really hours away quarantining with his mom or if he's been lying to her.
